Alembic Migration Directory for CG SCF Backend
==============================================

This directory contains database migration scripts managed by Alembic.

Directory Structure:
- env.py          : Alembic environment configuration (async SQLAlchemy)
- script.py.mako  : Template for generating new migration files
- versions/       : Migration scripts (timestamped and revision-numbered)

Quick Commands (run from backend/ directory):
- alembic upgrade head     : Apply all pending migrations
- alembic downgrade -1     : Roll back the last migration
- alembic revision -m "..."  : Create a new manual migration
- alembic revision --autogenerate -m "..."  : Generate migration from model changes
- alembic history          : Show migration history
- alembic current          : Show current database revision

For detailed documentation, see docs/MIGRATIONS.md in the project root.
